        {
            "title": "半日收市︱先升後回 恒指跌26點報26559點 港地產股揚升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股今早高開後反覆回吐，半日轉跌收市，「三桶油」全線造好，香港地產股再度揚升，九龍倉置業(01997)、新鴻基地產(00016)等齊創52周新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_01997-Harbour-City-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_01997-Harbour-City-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數高開165點後於初段曾再上層樓，但升幅擴大至194點、衝上26779點後便乏力再上，中段曾倒跌最多85點，見半日低位26499點，其後進入好淡爭持階段，升跌僅在數十點之內。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指中午收報26559點，跌26點或0.1%。恒生科技指數相對跑輸，跌23點或0.41%，報5722點；國企指數跌30點或0.34%，報9091點。主板半日成交1316.28億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指半日跌8點，報26562點，高水4點。科指期貨跌21點，報5729點，高水6點。國指期貨跌24點，報9095點，高水3點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際石油市場供應趨緊有利支持油價，「三桶油」借勢向上。中國石油(00857)升3.45%，報8.69元；中國石化(00386)也升3.21%，報5.1元，創52周新高；中海油(00883)升3.07%，報22.86元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本地地產股再次發力，九龍倉置業登上藍籌升幅榜首，半日升4.33%，報26.48元；新地升3.72%，報114.3元；長實集團(01113)亦創52周新高，報44.08元，升1.85%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">百度(09888)是表現最佳藍籌科股，半日升4.16%，報160.1元。該股昨天已獲多家券商唱好，再加上百度今日正式發布文心大模型5.0正式版，亦成為推動該股氣氛的原因之一。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15602844-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%85%88%e5%8d%87%e5%be%8c%e5%9b%9e-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c26%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126559%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b8%af%e5%9c%b0%e7%94%a2%e8%82%a1%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 12:30:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市反覆爭持 石油行業較受捧",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市今早輕微高開後轉好淡爭持，半日倒跌收場，各主要板塊升多於跌，石油行業表現較突出，中海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)曾漲近6%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中海油官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-175104__source-web_00883.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中海油官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-175104__source-web_00883.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中海油官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指高開9點後於初段原本一直向好，最高見4140點，漲23點，但在早市中段動力卻突降，短暫倒跌約4點、見4112點後曾收復失地，尾市再度轉跌；滬指中午收報4110點，跌6點或0.15%，半日成交7986.55億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指早市亦呈反覆偏軟格局，初段最高見14374點，升121點，其後升幅逐漸收窄且於中段一度倒跌，其後雖然略為反彈，尾市卻再度尋底，但最多只跌31點，報14223點；深指中午收報14230點，跌24點或0.17%，成交9749.07億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌21點或0.46%，收報4701點；創業板指數跌13點或0.4%，報3282點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際石油市場供應趨緊有利支持油價，A股市場的石油行業板塊今早乘勢跑出。「三桶油」全線向上，中海油A股最高曾衝上32.39元，漲5.99%，中午收報31.93元，仍升4.48%；中國石化(00386)A股(600028.SH)升3.36%，報6.16元；中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)升1.3%，報10.13元。石化油服(01033)A股(600871.SH)更漲7.53%，報2.57元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光伏股也現炒作，鈞達股份(02865)剛配售H股集資，今早一樣A、H齊漲，H股早段最多曾飆逾16%，鈞達股份A股(002865.SZ)亦升約10%漲停板，報90.4元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15602672-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e7%9f%b3%e6%b2%b9%e8%a1%8c%e6%a5%ad%e8%bc%83%e5%8f%97%e6%8d%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 11:40:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股顯著反彈　一度升逾千點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股顯著反彈，結束5日跌勢。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數升幅一度擴大至逾千點，半日報53760點，升986點，升幅1.87%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15602610-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e9%a1%af%e8%91%97%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88%e3%80%80%e4%b8%80%e5%ba%a6%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be%e5%8d%83%e9%bb%9e-2",
