            "title": "中國船舶租賃發23.38億元換股債 股價初段受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國船舶租賃(03877)今早公布，擬發行23.38億元換股債；該股初段應聲受壓，截至上午約9時45分跌4.93%，報2.12元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國船舶租賃官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03877-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國船舶租賃官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03877-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國船舶租賃官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述換股價為5年期，年息0.75%；初步換股價2.39元，較該股昨天收市價2.23元溢價7.17%，較前5個交易日平均收價2.25元溢價6.22%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">預期集資淨額約23.22億元，用作營運資金及一般企業用途，包括但不限於償還現有貸款、支付船舶購置費用及其他借貸成本。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15602262-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%88%b9%e8%88%b6%e7%a7%9f%e8%b3%83%e7%99%bc23-38%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e6%8f%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%82%b5-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03877-Web2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 09:50:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英諾賽科董事長自願作12個月禁售承諾 股價今早應聲向上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英諾賽科(02577)公布，董事長兼執行董事、控股股東集團成員Weiwei Luo博士自願作出禁售承諾，於未來12個月不減持。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：英諾賽科官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source-web_02577-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：英諾賽科官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source-web_02577-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：英諾賽科官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早應聲向上，截至上午約9時35分報66.2元，升6.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Weiwei Luo現時持有1.55億股英諾賽科，當中半數是境內未上市股份，半數是H股。公告指出，今次自願禁售是基於Weiwei Luo對公司未來發展的信心，以及長遠投資價值的充分認同。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15602256-%e8%8b%b1%e8%ab%be%e8%b3%bd%e7%a7%91%e8%91%a3%e4%ba%8b%e9%95%b7%e8%87%aa%e9%a1%98%e4%bd%9c12%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e7%a6%81%e5%94%ae%e6%89%bf%e8%ab%be-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e6%87%89",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source-web_02577-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 09:40:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
